author: By BRIAN MELLEY and CUNEYT DIL Associated Press
title: California swamped by jobless claims; LA virus cases rise
description: LOS ANGELES (AP) — California hired retired state workers and transferred other employees to help process an avalanche of over 1 million unemployment claims amid a surge of job losses from the coronavirus pandemic, the state said Thursday.
